Package: svyplan
Type: Package
Title: Survey Sample Size Determination
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Ahmadou",
                  family = "Dicko",
                  email = "mail@ahmadoudicko.com",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9654-7582"),
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for survey sample size determination, optimal
    allocation, stratification, and power analysis. Computes sample sizes
    for proportions and means, optimal multistage cluster allocations,
    variance components from frame data, design effects, optimal strata
    boundaries, and statistical power for two-sample tests.
    Based on methods from Cochran (1977, ISBN:978-0-471-16240-7),
    Kish (1965, ISBN:978-0-471-48900-9), and Valliant, Dever, and Kreuter
    (2018, ISBN:978-3-319-93630-4).
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    stats
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    survey,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
